# CNG workflow: native projects are NOT uploaded. EAS Build runs `expo prebuild`
# to regenerate android/ (and ios/) fresh for the current Expo SDK on every build.
# (.easignore takes precedence over .gitignore for what EAS uploads, so /android
#  must be listed here too — otherwise a stale local android/ would be uploaded.)
/android
/ios

# Build outputs / caches / artifacts
.expo/
*.apk
*.aab
*.keystore
